 Aisha Yesufu Nigerian Activist, Aisha Yesufu has revealed that she her life is being threatened by anonymous persons. Reacting to the threats she received, Aisha stated that “We are all going to die and it can be TODAY!” asking if the pandemic hasn’t taught them anything. She also added that “Killing me means I have seriously dealt with you!
I was born to die! Try something else!” For real someone threatened me?! ????? With death? Same death that is almost dozen for one kobo? Haven't the pandemic taught them anything? We are all going to die and it can be TODAY!Killing me means I have seriously dealt with you!I was born to die! Try something else! — Aisha Yesufu (@AishaYesufu) February 2, 2021